177 A.3d 116 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. ALEXIS ANDERSON, A/K/A ALEXIS ALLEN ANDERSON, ALEXANDER ANDERSON, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-416 September Term 2017

079667 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003728-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
